				<lb facs='#facs_1_region_1603268463034_588l1' n='N001'/>Kiss József
			</p>
			<p facs='#facs_1_region_1603268464893_591'>
				<lb facs='#facs_1_region_1603268464893_591l1' n='N001'/><unclear>I</unclear> Évfolyam
